    "text": "I was like, wow, I'm from the US."
  },
  {
    "start": 529.6,
    "text": "So it may come a lot easy, but no, I was humbled."
  },
  {
    "start": 533.2,
    "text": "I mentioned before too that some of the wording of the questions"
  },
  {
    "start": 538.8,
    "text": "and the answers and the text is a bit unnatural."
  },
  {
    "start": 542.0,
    "text": "I think it's good to know these advanced vocabulary words"
  },
  {
    "start": 545.6,
    "text": "for when you do have to take tests like this."
  },
  {
    "start": 548.0,
    "text": "But we would not use it in conversation."
  },
  {
    "start": 550.8,
    "text": "So I would not say maybe even half of the things that were in this test."
  },
  {
    "start": 555.2,
    "text": "So I think it's important that if you actually want to communicate"
